@Par.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5158

### Get All Boxes (with pagination)
GET {{Par.Api_HostAddress}}/api/boxes?page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Box by ID
GET {{Par.Api_HostAddress}}/api/boxes/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new Box
POST {{Par.Api_HostAddress}}/api/boxes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "size": 1,
  "customWeight": 3.5,
  "author": "Manager",
  "weightRangeMin": 10,
  "weightRangeMax": 500,
  "products": [
    {
      "name": "Product A",
      "type": 0,
      "weight": 2.5,
      "quantity": 3
    },
    {
      "name": "Product B",
      "type": 1,
      "weight": 1.8,
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

###

### Update a Box (PUT - replaces all data)
PUT {{Par.Api_HostAddress}}/api/boxes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "size": 2,
  "customWeight": 4.2,
  "author": "Operator",
  "weightRangeMin": 15,
  "weightRangeMax": 600,
  "products": [
    {
      "name": "Updated Product",
      "type": 2,
      "weight": 3.0,
      "quantity": 5
    }
  ]
}

###

### Partially Update a Box (PATCH - only specified fields)
PATCH {{Par.Api_HostAddress}}/api/boxes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customWeight": 5.0,
  "author": "Manager"
}

###

### Delete a Box
DELETE {{Par.Api_HostAddress}}/api/boxes/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Export All Boxes to CSV
GET {{Par.Api_HostAddress}}/api/boxes/export
Accept: text/csv

###

### Benchmark Export Performance
GET {{Par.Api_HostAddress}}/api/boxes/benchmark
Accept: application/json

